<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .header { background: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 24px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 24px; }
    .badge { background: #e0e7ff; color: #4f46e5; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 13px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 16px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 12px; padding: 16px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Daily Learning Package</h1>
    <p>{{subject}} — {{dateStr}}</p>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Your <strong>{{subject}}</strong> daily learning package for <strong>{{dateStr}}</strong> is ready!</p>
    <p>It includes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Top questions from today's class with model answers</li>
      <li>Short answers for quick revision</li>
      <li>Detailed explanations</li>
      <li>Real-life examples</li>
      <li>A quick quiz to test yourself</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <a href="{{pdfUrl}}" class="btn">Download PDF</a>
    </p>
    <p style="color:#666; font-size:13px;">The download link is valid for 1 hour. You can also access all your packages from your student profile.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">Top Tutors — Personalized Learning</div>
</body>
</html>
